Includes McCaw Method bag















MM REGENERATION PACK 
































The key to better performances is better recovery. The McCaw Method Regeneration pack is a must for any athlete who wants to stay healthy, loose and ready to perform without pain. The pack includes the MM roller stick for myo fascial release, a trigger point ball for getting in to those ‘hot spots and knots' and the MM stretch strap to increase flexibility and range of motion (ROM).

                                    
Contents


MM Roller stick
MM Stretch strap 
Trigger point ball
Includes McCaw Method travel bag















MM STRETCH STRAP























Discounted rates for orders over 12 pieces. Please contact mccawmethod@aol.com









The number 1 selling product, and used by some of the very best athletes in the world, the MM Stretch Strap is the design of leading Sports Performance specialist Allistair McCaw. Having worked with all levels of athletes, McCaw discovered that many injuries were connected to the athlete having limited mobility and flexibility in the hips caused by muscle-tendon unit tightness. This method of stretching, opens up the hip, creating more flexibility and mobility to the surrounding muscles and joints.
Benefits to the Athlete

Improves hip mobility & flexibility
Reduces injury risk
Maintains and improves range of motion




















MM RESISTANCE TUBE FOR TENNIS/SQUASH
































Tennis & Squash are physically demanding games and a good warm up is vital. The MM resistance tube comes with one of two McCaw Method programs that each include 18 specific exercises designed either for Tennis or Squash. These programs includes the Warm up, Prehab and Strength routines. The best players in the world warm up like this, so now it's your turn!

                                    
Benefits to the Athlete


Reduces injury risk
High quality product built to last
Stay supple, but strong


















MM 12" HALF-FOAM ROLLER
































One of Allistair’s favorite pieces of equipment. The 'MM half foam roller' is perfect for unilateral leg strength training, developing core stabilization and lower body balance.

                                    
Benefits to the Athlete


Improves ankle/foot mobility
Improves balance and core stabilization
Ideal for unilateral leg training
12" size is perfect size and weight for traveling

















MM PERFORMANCE T-SHIRT
































The McCaw Method Performance T-shirt has an ultra-lightweight feel and superior performance. It helps you stay comfortable and dry while reducing skin irritation from chafing or seam stacking. It wicks sweat away from the skin, where it evaporates quickly keeping you cool and dry.

                                    
