MM ULTRASLIDE



























                                        UltraSlide slideboards are the highest quality sliding boards available. The Ultraslide® is the leading slideboard used by some of the best athletes and trainers in the world. Allistair McCaw, believes that the Ultraslide is one of the best tools to improve an athletes lateral speed, leg strength, balance and co-ordination skills. In fact, he has used this form of training to prepare some of the world’s best Grand Slam tennis champions and Olympians before competition.

                                    
 





















